refersReducedMotion\r\n```\r\n\r\nShould be set to true, as we use Claude Code in docker or autonomous mode.\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\nshowThinkingSummaries\r\n```\r\n\r\nShould be set to false by default. To reduce load on the system. \r\n\r\n`spinnerTipsEnabled` to false\r\n\r\n`viewMode` to `verbose`.\r\n\r\n```\r\nenv\r\n```\r\n\r\nsetting should be set to all the same default variables.\r\n\r\n```\r\nCLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_FAST_MODE\r\n```\r\n\r\nShould be disabled, meaning = 1.\r\n\r\nDouble check `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_FEEDBACK_SURVEY ` is disabled.\r\n\r\nCLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_MOUSE also should be set to 1.\r\n\r\nCLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_AWAY_SUMMARY should be disabled.\r\n\r\nCLAUDE_CODE_MAX_TOOL_USE_CONCURRENCY should be set to 4.\r\n\r\nhttps://code.claude.com/docs/en/env-vars - we should double check what other ENVs we should consider to set for our automated environment. Please report me for options, and I will select what else to configure. Also check json settings docs.\r\n\r\nWe need to ensure all changes are correct, consistent, validated, tested, logged and fully meet each and all discussed requirements (check issue description and all comments in issue and in pull request). Ensure all CI/CD checks pass.","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/comments/4274073911/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/comments/4274083482","html_url":"https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/pull/1643#issuecomment-4274083482","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/1643","id":4274083482,"node_id":"IC_kwDOPUU0qc7-wVaa","user":{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard"