[2026-04-18T16:15:31.615Z] [STDOUT] {"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/pulls/1643","id":3550055441,"node_id":"PR_kwDOPUU0qc7TmYwR","html_url":"https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/pull/1643","diff_url":"https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/pull/1643.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/pull/1643.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/link-assistant/hive-mind/issues/1643","number":1643,"state":"open","locked":false,"title":"Disable noisy Claude Code features in solve","user":{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard","html_url":"https://github.com/konard","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"## Summary\n\nFixes #1642.\n\nThis PR makes Claude Code runs launched by `solve` quieter and more deterministic:\n\n- Adds `src/claude-quiet-config.lib.mjs` with the required quiet settings/env map and a merge helper for `~/.claude/settings.json`.\n- Verifies/merges the global Claude settings before launching Claude, preserving unrelated settings and unrelated `env` entries.\n- Forces the six required env vars into the Claude subprocess environment via `getClaudeEnv()`.\n- Bakes the same env vars and baseline `settings.json` values into both `Dockerfile` and `coolify/Dockerfile`.\n- Adds a patch changeset and a regression test wired into `npm test`.\n- Saves issue/PR data and external Claude Code documentation snapshots under `docs/case-studies/issue-1642/`.\n\n## Reproduction\n\nBefore the fix, the new focused regression failed because `getClaudeEnv()` did not force the required quiet env vars:\n\n```text\nAssertionError [ERR_ASSERTION]: getClaudeEnv should force CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_AUTO_MEMORY=1\nundefined !== '1'\n```\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node tests/test-claude-quiet-config.mjs`\n- `node tests/useless-tools.test.mjs`\n- `npm test`\n- `npm run format:check`\n- `npm run lint`\n- `npm run check:duplication`\n- `bash scripts/check-file-line-limits.sh` after removing local `node_modules/`, matching CI job order\n- `node scripts/validate-changeset.mjs`\n- `node tests/docs-validation.mjs`\n- `node --check src/solve.mjs`\n- `node --check src/hive.mjs`\n- `bash scripts/check-mjs-syntax.sh`\n\n## Notes\n\nNo screenshots are included because this is runtime/Docker configuration work, not a UI change.\n","created_at":"2026-04-18T15:09:05Z","updated_at":"2026-04-18T16:15:29Z","closed_at":null,"merged_at":null,"merge_commit_sha":"b4fb9ff82d910808d49a71d41dee7b3ae92ba695","assignees":[{"login":"konard","id":1431904,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1431904?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard","html_url":"https://github.com/konard","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/konard/repos","events_url":"ht