[2026-04-18T16:17:04.279Z] [INFO]         "content": "# Complete Environment Variables List\n\nHere are ALL environment variables mentioned in the documentation:\n\n## Authentication & API\n- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` - API key for Anthropic authentication\n- `ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN` - Custom Authorization header value\n- `ANTHROPIC_BETAS` - Comma-separated beta header values\n- `ANTHROPIC_CUSTOM_HEADERS` - Custom headers for API requests\n- `ANTHROPIC_FOUNDRY_API_KEY` - API key for Microsoft Foundry authentication\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN` - OAuth access token for Claude.ai authentication\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_REFRESH_TOKEN` - OAuth refresh token for Claude.ai\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_SCOPES` - Space-separated OAuth scopes\n- `AWS_BEARER_TOKEN_BEDROCK` - Bedrock API key for authentication\n\n## API Endpoints & Routing\n- `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` - Override API endpoint (proxy/gateway routing)\n- `ANTHROPIC_BEDROCK_BASE_URL` - Override Bedrock endpoint URL\n- `ANTHROPIC_BEDROCK_MANTLE_BASE_URL` - Override Bedrock Mantle endpoint URL\n- `ANTHROPIC_FOUNDRY_BASE_URL` - Full Foundry resource base URL\n- `ANTHROPIC_FOUNDRY_RESOURCE` - Foundry resource name\n- `ANTHROPIC_VERTEX_BASE_URL` - Override Vertex AI endpoint URL\n- `ANTHROPIC_VERTEX_PROJECT_ID` - GCP project ID for Vertex AI\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_IDE_HOST_OVERRIDE` - Override IDE extension connection host\n\n## Model Configuration\n- `ANTHROPIC_MODEL` - Model name setting to use\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL` - Custom Haiku model ID\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL_NAME` - Display name for Haiku model\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL_DESCRIPTION` - Description for Haiku model\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL_SUPPORTED_CAPABILITIES` - Haiku capabilities\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL` - Custom Opus model ID\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL_NAME` - Display name for Opus model\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL_DESCRIPTION` - Description for Opus model\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL_SUPPORTED_CAPABILITIES` - Opus capabilities\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL` - Custom Sonnet model ID\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL_NAME` - Display name for Sonnet model\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL_DESCRIPTION` - Description for Sonnet model\n- `ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL_SUPPORTED_CAPABILITIES` - Sonnet capabilities\n- `ANTHROPIC_CUSTOM_MODEL_OPTION` - Custom model ID for model picker\n- `ANTHROPIC_CUSTOM_MODEL_OPTION_NAME` - Display name for custom model\n- `ANTHROPIC_CUSTOM_MODEL_OPTION_DESCRIPTION` - Description for custom model\n- `ANTHROPIC_CUSTOM_MODEL_OPTION_SUPPORTED_CAPABILITIES` - Custom model capabilities\n- `ANTHROPIC_SMALL_FAST_MODEL` - [DEPRECATED] Haiku-class model for background tasks\n- `ANTHROPIC_SMALL_FAST_MODEL_AWS_REGION` - AWS region override for Haiku model\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SUBAGENT_MODEL` - Model for subagents\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_USE_BEDROCK` - Use Bedrock\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_USE_FOUNDRY` - Use Microsoft Foundry\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_USE_VERTEX` - Use Vertex AI\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_USE_MANTLE` - Use Bedrock Mantle endpoint\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SKIP_BEDROCK_AUTH` - Skip AWS authentication for Bedrock\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SKIP_FOUNDRY_AUTH` - Skip Azure authentication for Foundry\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SKIP_MANTLE_AUTH` - Skip AWS authentication for Mantle\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SKIP_VERTEX_AUTH` - Skip Google authentication for Vertex\n\n## Performance & Timeouts\n- `API_TIMEOUT_MS` - Timeout for API requests in milliseconds (default: 600000)\n- `BASH_DEFAULT_TIMEOUT_MS` - Default timeout for bash commands (default: 120000)\n- `BASH_MAX_TIMEOUT_MS` - Maximum timeout for bash commands (default: 600000)\n- `BASH_MAX_OUTPUT_LENGTH` - Maximum characters in bash outputs before truncation\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_GLOB_TIMEOUT_SECONDS` - Timeout for Glob tool file discovery (default: 20s)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_PLUGIN_GIT_TIMEOUT_MS` - Timeout for plugin git operations (default: 120000)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SYNC_PLUGIN_INSTALL_TIMEOUT_MS` - Timeout for synchronous plugin installation\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SESSIONEND_HOOKS_TIMEOUT_MS` - Time budget for SessionEnd hooks\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_OTEL_FLUSH_TIMEOUT_MS` - Timeout for flushing OpenTelemetry spans (default: 5000)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_OTEL_SHUTDOWN_TIMEOUT_MS` - Timeout for OTel exporter shutdown (default: 2000)\n\n## Concurrency & Resource Control\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_MAX_TOOL_USE_CONCURRENCY` - Maximum parallel read-only tools/subagents (default: 10)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_MAX_RETRIES` - Number of API request retries (default: 10)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_MAX_CONTEXT_TOKENS` - Override context window size\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_MAX_OUTPUT_TOKENS` - Maximum output tokens for requests\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_FILE_READ_MAX_OUTPUT_TOKENS` - Token limit override for file reads\n- `MAX_THINKING_TOKENS` - Thinking budget (referenced indirectly)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_EFFORT_LEVEL` - Effort level for supported models (low/medium/high/xhigh/max/auto)\n\n## Context & Memory Management\n- `CLAUDE_AUTOCOMPACT_PCT_OVERRIDE` - Context capacity percentage for auto-compaction (1-100, default ~95%)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_AUTO_COMPACT_WINDOW` - Context capacity in tokens for auto-compaction calculations\n- `DISABLE_COMPACT` - Disable context auto-compaction (referenced indirectly)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_AUTO_MEMORY` - Disable auto memory (set to 1 to disable, 0 to force enable)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_CLAUDE_MDS` - Prevent loading CLAUDE.md memory files\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_CODE_ADDITIONAL_DIRECTORIES_CLAUDE_MD` - Load memory files from additional directories\n\n## Feature Toggles - DISABLE_*\n- `DISABLE_TELEMETRY` - Disable telemetry\n- `DISABLE_AUTOUPDATER` - Disable auto-updater\n- `DISABLE_ERROR_REPORTING` - Disable error reporting\n- `DISABLE_FEEDBACK_COMMAND` - Disable feedback command\n\n## Feature Toggles - CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_*\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_1M_CONTEXT` - Disable 1M context window support\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_ADAPTIVE_THINKING` - Disable adaptive reasoning on Opus/Sonnet 4.6\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_ATTACHMENTS` - Disable attachment processing\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_BACKGROUND_TASKS` - Disable background task functionality\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_CRON` - Disable scheduled tasks\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_EXPERIMENTAL_BETAS` - Strip anthropic-beta headers from requests\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_FAST_MODE` - Disable fast mode\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_FEEDBACK_SURVEY` - Disable session quality surveys\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_FILE_CHECKPOINTING` - Disable file checkpointing\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_GIT_INSTRUCTIONS` - Remove git workflow instructions from system prompt\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_LEGACY_MODEL_REMAP` - Prevent remapping of Opus 4.0/4.1\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_MOUSE` - Disable mouse tracking in fullscreen\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC` - Disable auto-updater, feedback, error reporting, telemetry\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONSTREAMING_FALLBACK` - Disable non-streaming fallback on stream failure\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_OFFICIAL_MARKETPLACE_AUTOINSTALL` - Skip auto-installation of official plugin marketplace\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_TERMINAL_TITLE` - Disable automatic terminal title updates\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_THINKING` - Force-disable extended thinking\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_VIRTUAL_SCROLL` - Disable virtual scrolling in fullscreen\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_OFFICIAL_MARKETPLACE_AUTOINSTALL` - Skip auto-add of official plugin marketplace\n\n## Feature Toggles - CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_*\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_AWAY_SUMMARY` - Override session recap availability\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_BACKGROUND_PLUGIN_REFRESH` - Refresh plugin state after background install\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_FINE_GRAINED_TOOL_STREAMING` - Force-enable fine-grained tool input streaming\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_PROMPT_SUGGESTION` - Enable/disable prompt suggestions\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_TASKS` - Enable task tracking in non-interactive mode\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_TELEMETRY` - Enable OpenTelemetry data collection\n\n## Background & Task Management\n- `CLAUDE_AUTO_BACKGROUND_TASKS` - Force-enable automatic backgrounding of long-running tasks\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_BACKGROUND_PLUGIN_REFRESH` - Refresh plugin state after background install completes\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_ENABLE_TASKS` - Enable task tracking in non-interactive mode\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_EXIT_AFTER_STOP_DELAY` - Time to wait before auto-exit after idle\n\n## Tools & Plugin Management\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_GLOB_HIDDEN` - Include dotfiles in Glob tool results (default: true)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_GLOB_NO_IGNORE` - Make Glob tool respect .gitignore patterns (default: false)\n- `CLAUDE_AGENT_SDK_DISABLE_BUILTIN_AGENTS` - Disable built-in subagent types (SDK only)\n- `CLAUDE_AGENT_SDK_MCP_NO_PREFIX` - Skip mcp__ prefix on tool names (SDK only)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_PLUGIN_CACHE_DIR` - Override plugins root directory\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_PLUGIN_KEEP_MARKETPLACE_ON_FAILURE` - Keep marketplace cache on git pull failure\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_PLUGIN_SEED_DIR` - Pre-populate plugins directory for containers\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SYNC_PLUGIN_INSTALL` - Wait for plugin installation in non-interactive mode\n\n## Environment & Execution\n- `CLAUDECODE` - Set to 1 in shell environments spawned by Claude Code\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SHELL` - Override automatic shell detection\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SHELL_PREFIX` - Command prefix to wrap all bash commands\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_GIT_BASH_PATH` - Windows only: path to Git Bash executable\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_USE_POWERSHELL_TOOL` - Control PowerShell tool availability\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_TMPDIR` - Override temp directory path\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SUBPROCESS_ENV_SCRUB` - Strip credentials from subprocess environments\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SCRIPT_CAPS` - JSON object limiting script invocations per session\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_PERFORCE_MODE` - Enable Perforce-aware write protection\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_BASH_MAINTAIN_PROJECT_WORKING_DIR` - Return to original working directory after commands\n\n## Terminal & UI\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_NO_FLICKER` - Enable fullscreen rendering (research preview)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_SCROLL_SPEED` - Mouse wheel scroll multiplier (1-20)\n- `CLAUDE_CODE_CODE_ACCESSIBILITY` - Keep terminal cursor visible, disable inverted-text cursor\n- `CLAUDE_COD