[2026-04-18T16:18:19.802Z] [INFO]     "oldString": "# Quiet, deterministic Claude Code defaults for autonomous solve runs (issue #1642)\nENV CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_AUTO_MEMORY=1 \\\n    CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_CRON=1 \\\n    CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_TERMINAL_TITLE=1 \\\n    CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_CLAUDE_MDS=1 \\\n    CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_GIT_INSTRUCTIONS=1 \\\n    DISABLE_FEEDBACK_COMMAND=1",
